float height = 0.;
for (float i = 0.; i < 5.; i++) {
float c = craters(0.4 * pow(2.2, i) * p);
float noise = 0.4 * exp(-3. * c) * FBM(10. * p);
float w = clamp(3. * pow(0.4, i), 0., 1.);
height += w * (c + noise);
}
height = pow(height, 3.);
